CocktailLife Website

Hey,

Here are the command lines necessary to make it work!

	npm install --save express mongoose nunjucks bulma
	npm i --save-dev dotenv nodemon

Also need to creat a .env file containing : DATABASE_URL=mongodb://localhost/CLdb

here are some information about the databse :
	name : CLdb
	table : [recipes]
You will find some data in the data.json file to populate the table.

Then to launch app :
	npm run devStart
